Bank Management System:

A modular console-based banking application developed in Python to simulate real-world financial operations with structured architecture and secure transaction handling.

Features:
- Open New Bank Account
- Delete Existing Account
- Deposit Money
- Withdraw Money
- View Account Details
- View All Accounts
- Search Account
- Generate PIN
- Update PIN
Technologies Used:
- Python
- File Handling
- Modular Programming
- Exception Handling

